== Welcome to My Music

The objective of this project is to share music tracks.
The user can add songs to his list through simple search.
Currently sharing can be done through json webservice available to public.

== Specific Gems

1. Devise - for authentication
2. Nifty - for quick layout

== Instructions for setup

you need to set up default url options for the mailer in each environment. 

Here is the configuration for config/environments/development.rb:
config.action_mailer.default_url_options = { :host => 'localhost:3000' }


